Package com.intel.inde.mp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAudioEffect
    This simple interface should be used for implementation of audio effects which could be embedded into MediaComposer pipeline
    IProgressListener
    Listener that notifies when composer changes state
    IRecognitionPlugin
    This interface is defined for recognition plug-in which could be embedded into pipelines to extract any type metadata supported by implementation by analyzing the received content
    IRecognitionPlugin.RecognitionEvent
    interface for signaling of recognition results
    IVideoEffect
    This simple interface should be used for implementation of video effects which could be embedded into MediaComposer pipeline
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioFormat
    This class is used to describe/setup parameters of audio data
    CameraCapture
    This class allows to stream data from the camera to the server or same video to file
    GLCapture
    Captures and encodes EGL scene to video file or to network stream
    IRecognitionPlugin.RecognitionInput
    Base class for input data supplied to recognition plug-in
    IRecognitionPlugin.RecognitionOutput
    Base class for output data received from recognition plug-in
    MediaComposer
    MediaComposer class for lite video editing and transcoding: files joining, cut segments from files, effect applying
    MediaFile
    This class contains all info about input media file: tracks formats, duration, segments with selected data
    MediaFileInfo
    This class provides information about media file and returns uncompressed video frame at selected position
    MediaStreamer
    This class allows to stream local media file to the server
    StreamingParameters
    This class is used to describe/setup parameters of streaming server
    Uri
    This class is used to store and pass Uri references which conform to RFC 2396 in String form
    VideoFormat
    This class is used to describe/setup parameters of video data
